Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)}#12 ONE NlGHT STAND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡力林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算世界灭亡了\n那大叔也不会死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陆上自卫队的96式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉萨\n用单分子切割刀瞄准姆指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在正…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver，B机能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，来试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，就是盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有发现到我对你的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟钝的泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果在那个时候\n杀了琢磨的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人就会放弃启动那架贝希摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然得不到，那就摧毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎，坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来推，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你驾驶了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人，增援呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想办法解决那个巨人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能逃得出我的手掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能够阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长，真高兴您没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德加斯，现在潜舰来到哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪伊半岛南方120公里附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急配置的喷射器也在射程外\n(AS射出用装置)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用弹道飞弹把Arbalest(强弩兵)送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备时间最少也要花一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在送达前的这一两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个巨人贝希摩斯不知道\n会给这城市带来多大的损害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没办法，我已经无计可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长，现在的情势\n需要Arbalest(强弩兵)吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有得到您许可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是载有Arbalest(强弩兵)的弹道飞弹\n已经准备好可在3分钟内发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射后约6分钟\n大概就能抵达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说\n需要花费9分钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有觉悟接受处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，你做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落地点呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落后可能会随即遭到巨人攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要更复杂的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着陆后能够争取出数十秒的时间\n让驾驶可以过去搭乘的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视野不要太辽阔比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不能在闹区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把平民卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照明较暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且是限定的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最好也能有高低差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最适合的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够充分发挥\nArbalest(强弩兵)能力的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它要开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到我叫你就转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它再瞄准一点打过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小货车可是撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，让车子一直线向前跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给那家伙一点颜色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗，绝对要一直线喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度也不要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，瞄准我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右头部火神炮损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱爆回避完毕\N我…我的贝希摩斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右头部火神炮无法使用\N竟敢伤了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼，交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你只是个\n光说不练的软弱家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要安心还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝希摩斯…启动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要破坏它是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料可以撑40个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前，没人能够阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要看琢磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得对不起他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为记忆混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时竟把我当成\n被他亲手杀死的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就凭着这点利用了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就没有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不问我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种好像什么都知道的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直让人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁・赛格维奇・卡力林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，还以为死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲吧，冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间笑的话就再开一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样动来动去怎么射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个，之前也有看过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了，被看得清清楚楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，还没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架机体不会这么简单就坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转弯，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以煞车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，会怎样我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛6号呼叫野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在拖拖拉拉个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手动操纵杆被压在地板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法强制打开容器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法打破蛋壳是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成炒蛋的话\n就都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要诅咒你\n直到你的子孙十八代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有最后一枚手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面，里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲破铁卷门进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有过这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃吧，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver，A机能低落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨骼系发生干扰波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，得集中精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啦，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会去问你姐姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在猎物面前舔舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是三流的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当你的对手，过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能…好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷…冷却？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把巨人的其中一个冷却装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES，士官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体有搭载λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设敌机有搭载λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可以对抗它的手段吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以现场士官的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把意识…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右膝盖连接部损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我搞不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过脚的连结部分好像有\nλ-Driver的冷却装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击那个地方，大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不能用普通的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那上面有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上校大人说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说泰莎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的回答怎么这么随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要觉得很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来所要发射的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会贯穿它的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么的相信才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，就像那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一条细长的隙缝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右哪边都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会中…一定要打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver机能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回复的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝希摩斯因重量过重开始分解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这种事有时也会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，的确很过份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系，琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，安心的λ睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了，威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的技术还是一样的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体已经是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你好好珍惜它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…小要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要特别感谢你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能好好说明一下这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，改天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，我能跟你宣言一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良士官\n把听觉传感器全部关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像喜欢上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…我…\n泰莎，泰莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是跟你说一声\n“我们互相加油吧”好了，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚吃红豆饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡力林他们似乎平安无事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我说，梅莉萨竟然看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是泰莎你自己先找我麻烦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅，我要跟你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，我会好好疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\n「猫与小猫的R&R(ROCK AND ROLL)」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:24.14,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,在\N心\N中\N绽\N开\N着\N一\N朵\N小\N花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:35.79,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N给\N我\N的\N那\N朵\N不\N会\N枯\N萎\N的\N花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:42.84,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,让\N我\N不\N再\N畏\N惧\N相\N信\N他\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:49.64,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,因\N此\N变\N得\N更\N坚\N强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:55.94,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,能\N与\N你\N相\N遇\N\N真\N的\N很\N高\N兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:22:02.54,edch,NTP,0,0,0,,能\N与\N你\N牵\N手\N\N是\N我\N的\N骄\N傲
